org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace

Class ConsensusAceTagBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace.ConsensusAceTagBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Builder<ConsensusAceTag>

    public final class ConsensusAceTagBuilder
extends Object
implements Builder<ConsensusAceTag>
    ConsensusAceTagBuilder is a Builder that builds a new instance of ConsensusAceTag. We usually need a builder because we don't often have the complete metadata for the comment and private data when parsing an ace file line by line.
    Author:
    dkatzel

        public ConsensusAceTagBuilder(String id,
                              String type,
                              String creator,
                              Date creationDate,
                              Rangeable location,
                              boolean isTransient)
        Create a new ConsensusAceTagBuilder instance.
        Parameters:
        id - the id of this tag.
        type - the type.
        creator - who (or which program) created this tag.
        creationDate - the date this tag was created.
        location - the region on the consensus that this tag is tagging.
        isTransient - should this tag be persisted to the next ace version if this ace file is updated.
